@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
hide footbox
skinparam lifelineStyle solid
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "PingFang SC"
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam actorFontSize 18
skinparam participantFontSize 18
skinparam databaseFontSize 18
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "User" as USER
participant ":F̲r̲o̲n̲t̲e̲n̲d̲" as FE
participant ":F̲l̲a̲s̲k̲A̲P̲I̲" as API
participant ":L̲L̲M̲C̲l̲i̲e̲n̲t̲" as LLM
participant ":R̲e̲m̲o̲t̲e̲L̲L̲M̲" as REMOTE

USER -> FE: 点击生成
FE -> API: POST /api/generate
activate API
API -> LLM: generate(prompt)
activate LLM
LLM -> REMOTE: chat.completions
activate REMOTE
REMOTE --> LLM: 返回响应
deactivate REMOTE
LLM --> API: 返回测试代码
deactivate LLM
API --> FE: 返回结果
deactivate API
FE --> USER: 显示测试代码
@enduml
